Date:   Mon May 3 11:29:22 2010 -0400

    Refuse null keys in evhttp_parse_query()
    
    evhttp_parse_query() currently accepts empty keys, that don't make any
    sense.
    
    -Frank
    
    [From sourceforge patch 2995183]
    -Nick

